---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Toolkit"
  description="Toolkit is a small collection of private, browser-based tools for everyday social and creative tasks."
  path="/about"
>
  <main class="page-shell section prose">
    <h1>About Toolkit</h1>
    <p>
      Toolkit is a small online tools site for everyday tasks that should be fast, simple, and private. The goal is not to collect a huge pile of tools. The goal is to make a few useful tools that load quickly and explain exactly what they do.
    </p>
    <h2>Private by design</h2>
    <p>
      Tools are built to run locally in your browser whenever possible. For text tools, that means your input is transformed on your device and is not uploaded to a server.
    </p>
    <h2>Built for real use</h2>
    <p>
      Each tool page includes instructions, practical examples, and FAQ content so visitors from search can understand the tool before using it.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
